idden\"><main class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto\"><div class=\"mb-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight\">Refund Policy</h1><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-2xl\">Our refund policy and withdrawal rights</p></div></div></div><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto py-8 px-6 space-y-6\"><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">Overview</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\">Thank you for purchasing services from Take The Reins. This refund policy outlines when you may be entitled to withdraw a transaction and/or receive a refund, and how to request one.</p><p class=\"text-gray-300\">If local consumer protection laws provide you with rights that are more favorable than this policy, those rights will apply. Nothing in this policy limits your mandatory consumer rights.</p></div></article></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">1. Global Refund Policy</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2\"><li><strong>Non-Refundable Transactions:</strong> Unless required by applicable law, all transactions are non-refundable and non-exchangeable.</li><li><strong>Discretionary Refunds:</strong> Take The Reins may issue refunds on a discretionary basis or if you exercise an applicable statutory withdrawal right.</li><li><strong>Fraud Prevention:</strong> Refunds will not be issued where there is evidence of fraud, refund abuse, or other manipulative behavior.</li><li><strong>Access Termination:</strong> If you receive a refund, access to the relevant service will cease immediately.</li><li><strong>Request Timeline:</strong> Refund requests must be made within the applicable statutory or discretionary period.</li></ul></div></article></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">2. Country-Specific Withdrawal Rights</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\"><strong>European Union / EEA / Switzerland / United Kingdom:</strong></p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4\"><li>14-day statutory withdrawal right from digital content and service contracts</li><li>Applies to first payments and one-off purchases</li><li>Does not apply to subsequent subscription payments (except for annual UK subscriptions)</li><li>Does not apply to partially consumed digital content when you&#x27;ve consented to waive withdrawal rights</li></ul><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\"><strong>Turkey &amp; Israel:</strong></p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4\"><li>14-day statutory withdrawal right from digital content and service contracts</li></ul><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\"><strong>South Korea, Brazil, China &amp; Canada:</strong></p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4\"><li>7-day unconditional right to cancel digital services and receive a full refund</li></ul><p class=\"text-gray-300\"><strong>Singapore:</strong></p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2\"><li>5-day unconditional right to cancel digital services and receive a full refund</li></ul></div></article></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">3. How to Request a Refund or Withdrawal</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4 font-semibold\">To withdraw, cancel, and/or request a refund, contact support:</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4\"><li>Email: support@takethereins.com</li><li>Reference your transaction or receipt details</li><li>Clearly state the reason for your refund request</li></ul><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\"><strong>Processing:</strong></p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2\"><li>Refunds will be processed using the same payment method where possible</li><li>Processing occurs within 14 days of approval</li><li>Your transaction records will be reviewed to verify eligibility</li></ul></div></article></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">4. Subscription Cancellation</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\">You may cancel your subscription at any time to prevent future billing:</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4\"><li>Cancellation takes effect at the end of your current billing period</li><li>No further payments will be taken after cancellation</li><li>This does not affect your eligibility for withdrawal rights during statutory periods</li></ul><p class=\"text-gray-300\">To cancel, contact support@takethereins.com at any time.</p></div></article></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">5. Technical or Product Defects</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\">If you experience persistent technical issues or material defects that prevent access to services as described:</p><ol class=\"list-decimal list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4\"><li>Contact our support team at support@takethereins.com</li><li>Provide detailed information about the issue</li><li>Allow us to attempt to resolve the issue first</li><li>If unresolved, you may be eligible for a refund</li></ol><p class=\"text-gray-300\">Where there is evidence of a material technical defect, refunds will be issued in accordance with applicable consumer protection laws.</p></div></article></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">6. Discretionary Refunds</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\">Take The Reins may, at its sole discretion, issue a refund if requested within 14 days of your transaction date. Such requests are reviewed on a case-by-case basis.</p><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\">We may consider factors including:</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4\"><li>The nature of the service</li><li>The reason for your request</li><li>Usage or consumption of the service</li><li>Any applicable contractual terms</li></ul><p class=\"text-gray-300\">We may approve a refund in full, approve a partial refund, or decline the request. Any discretionary refund is voluntary and does not create an obligation to provide refunds in the future.</p></div></article></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">7. Add-Ons and One-Time Transactions</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2\"><li>Refund eligibility for add-ons and one-time transactions follows the same criteria as primary transactions</li><li>Add-ons expire when the main subscription ends unless otherwise stated</li><li>Items delivered and fully accessible immediately may be non-refundable once delivered (except where required by law)</li></ul></div></article></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">8. Chargebacks and Payment Disputes</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\">We encourage you to contact us before raising a chargeback or payment dispute:</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4\"><li>Contact support@takethereins.com first</li><li>Allow us to resolve the matter</li><li>This helps avoid service suspension and faster resolution</li></ul><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\">If you initiate a chargeback or payment dispute, your access to services may be temporarily suspended while we review the matter. This does not affect your lawful rights to dispute a charge under applicable law.</p></div></article></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">9. Consumer Rights Protection</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\">This policy does not affect your consumer rights in relation to services that are:</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2\"><li>Not as described</li><li>Faulty or defective</li><li>Not fit for the purpose described</li></ul></div></article></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">10. Policy Updates</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\">Take The Reins may update this policy at any time. The policy in effect at the time of your transaction governs that transaction.</p><p class=\"text-gray-300\">We recommend saving or printing a copy of this policy for your records.</p></div></article></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">Contact &amp; Support</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\">For questions about this refund policy or to request a refund:</p><p class=\"text-gray-300 font-semibold\">Email: support@takethereins.com</p><p class=\"text-gray-300 mt-4 text-sm\">Last Updated: March 18, 2026</p></div></article></section><div class=\"pt-8 flex gap-4\"><a href=\"/dashboard\"><button class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors\">← Back to Dashboard</button></a></div></div></main></div></div></div><script id=\"__NEXT_DATA__\" type=\"application/json\">{\"props\":{\"pageProps\":{}},\"page\":\"/dashboard/refund-policy\",\"query\":{},\"buildId\":\"wDAhdRrE5oh3YKiYu4_Cl\",\"nextExport\":true,\"autoExport\":true,\"isFallback\":false,\"scriptLoader\":[]}</script></body></html>","isFullyStaticPage":true}